OL,3,CTrump says he 'feels good' after
OL,4,CStrait of Hormuz 'fully open'
OL,6,FUS President Donald Trump said he
OL,7,F"feels good" about the Strait of
OL,8,FHormuz reopening, but that the US
OL,9,Fblockade will remain in place.
OL,11,FHe was speaking to ITV News' US
OL,12,FCorrespondent Dan Rivers on Friday
OL,13,Fshortly after a joint statement with
OL,14,FIranian Foreign Minister Abbas
OL,15,FAraghchi said the crucial Strait "is
OL,16,Ffully open and ready for full passage".
OL,18,FBut the Strait is not open as it
OL,19,Fpertains to Iran, Trump said, adding:
OL,20,F"We have to finish the deal before we
OL,21,Fopen it for Iran".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
