FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1776593186
OL,3,CTrump says he 'feels good' after
OL,4,CStrait of Hormuz 'fully open'
OL,6,FWhen asked where this leaves the US/UK
OL,7,Frelationship with Sir Keir Starmer, he
OL,8,Fresponded: "Not good, not good at all".
OL,10,FThe US President told ITV News that
OL,11,Fit's "too bad" he didn't receive any
OL,12,Fhelp from Nato on the re-opening of
OL,13,Fthe Strait, calling the alliance a
OL,14,F"paper tiger".
OL,16,FIn a post on Truth Social on Friday
OL,17,Fafternoon, Trump wrote: "The naval
OL,18,Fblockade will remain in full force and
OL,19,Feffect as it pretrains to Iran, only,
OL,20,Funtil such time as our transaction
OL,21,Fwith Iran is 100% complete".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
