PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1776593186
OL,3,CTrump says he 'feels good' after
OL,4,CStrait of Hormuz 'fully open'
OL,6,FMinutes earlier, Iranian Foreign
OL,7,FMinister Abbas Araghchi posted on the
OL,8,Fsocial platform X that the passage for
OL,9,Fall commercial vessels through the
OL,10,Fstrait "is declared completely open"
OL,11,Fin line with the ceasefire in Lebanon.
OL,13,FHe said it would stay open for the
OL,14,Fremaining period of the ceasefire.
OL,16,FCrude oil prices immediately tumbled
OL,17,F10% as a result.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/5
