OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1776593186
OL,3,CTrump says he 'feels good' after
OL,4,CStrait of Hormuz 'fully open'
OL,6,FThe Strait of Hormuz, a crucial
OL,7,Fshipping lane through which a fifth of
OL,8,Fthe world's oil normally flows, was
OL,9,Fclosed by Iran as a response to
OL,10,FAmerica and Israel's strikes.
OL,12,FIn retaliation, Trump had begun his
OL,13,Fown blockade of Iran's oil ports,
OL,14,Faimed at cutting off Tehran's fossil
OL,15,Ffuel income.
OL,17,FThis is a breaking news story and will
OL,18,Fbe updated.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/5
